==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|mī-kŏfʹə-gəs}}
===Adjective===
'''mycophagous'''
# [[fungus]]-eating.
===Etymology===
''myc(o)- + phag- + -ous'', from Greek ''mukēs'', fungus + Greek ''phagein'', to eat. The Latin equivalent is [[fungivorous]], from  fung- + -vor + -ous, from ''fungus'', fungus + ''vorāre'', to swallow, devour.

